lead_paragraph: Kazakhstan leads Serbia 2-1 in the first round of the Davis Cup after Andrey Golubev and Aleksandr Nedovyesov beat Novak Djokovic and Nenad Zimonjic 6-3, 7-6 (3), 7-5 in the doubles match.

headline.print_headline: Kazakhstan Leads Serbia 2-1 in Davis Cup After Doubles Win
